    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Roberto Waldteufel</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:287px;\"><a href=\"http://www.wylliedraughts.com/roberto.htm\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/b/be/RobertoWaldteufel.jpg\" width=\"285\" height=\"194\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:RobertoWaldteufel.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Roberto Waldteufel <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Roberto Waldteufel</b>, (born 13 Dec 1962)<br />\na French/British <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> computer games programmer born in Spain <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, living on the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jura,_Scotland\">Island of Jura, Scotland</a>. Roberto is author of the <a href=\"/Checkers\" title=\"Checkers\">Checkers</a> program <i>Wyllie</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, and the chess program <a href=\"/Rabbit\" title=\"Rabbit\">Rabbit</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. Roberto Waldteufel seemed the first one, who mentioned the optimization trick in 1998 to dense the <a href=\"/Rotated_Bitboards\" title=\"Rotated Bitboards\">Rotated Bitboards</a> tables, masking off the redundant <a href=\"/First_Rank_Attacks#TheOuterSquares\" title=\"First Rank Attacks\">outer occupancies</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1998_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1998 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roberto_Waldteufel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1998_...\">1998 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roberto_Waldteufel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1998 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=19733\">Rabbit beats heffalump with nice queen sac</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Roberto Waldteufel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 01, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=25740\">Re: Chess in BASIC?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Roberto Waldteufel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 31, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Basic\" title=\"Basic\">Basic</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=28772\">Null move reductions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Roberto Waldteufel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 04, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=30023\">Attack Tables</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Roberto Waldteufel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 20, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=30562\">Efficient Bitboard Implementation on 32-bit Architecture</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 25, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=30863\">Efficient Rotated Bitboard Representations</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Roberto Waldteufel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 28, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=31456\">Re: Extracting information from rotated Bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Roberto Waldteufel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 02, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=33136\">Rabbit available for download</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Roberto Waldteufel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 16, 1998</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roberto_Waldteufel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=107902\">Tablebase Access Code</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Roberto Waldteufel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 26, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=113078\">What is the Success Rate of Killer/History Moves?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Roberto Waldteufel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 31, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Killer_Heuristic\" title=\"Killer Heuristic\">Killer Heuristic</a> <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=391828\">Has Anybody got the Brainy.zip file from Dan Corbit's site?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Roberto Waldteufel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 16, 2004</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roberto_Waldteufel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.wylliedraughts.com/\">Wyllie Checkers Program</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chess.fsv.de/Summer98/descript.htm#Roberto%20Waldteufel\">Summer98-Tournament: Description</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Torsten_Schoop&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Torsten Schoop (page does not exist)\">Torsten Schoop</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roberto_Waldteufel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.wylliedraughts.com/roberto.htm\">About Wyllie's Programmer</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chess.fsv.de/Summer98/descript.htm#Roberto%20Waldteufel\">Summer98-Tournament: Description</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Torsten_Schoop&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Torsten Schoop (page does not exist)\">Torsten Schoop</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=23490\">Re: V Spanish MCC</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Roberto Waldteufel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 31, 1998</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.wylliedraughts.com/\">Wyllie Checkers Program</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=33136\">Rabbit available for download</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Roberto Waldteufel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 16, 1998</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=31456\">Extracting information from rotated Bitboards</a> by Roberto Waldteufel, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 02, 1998</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301085459\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.021 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 107/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 234/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:4762-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301085459 and revision id 9008\n -->\n"
